title: TorontoJS Tech Talks [ Online ] is back again!  Community Engagement!
details:
Details

TorontoJS Tech Talks [ Online ] is back again! Community Engagement!We're thrilled to announce the return of TorontoJS Tech Talks to the virtual stage! In this session, we're diving into the topic of community engagement!

Meet Our Special Guest, Our very own TorontoJS organizer Aman Aalam and Senior Developer Advocate @ Trolley!

Schedule:
6:00 pm - Warm welcome and introduction by TorontoJS
6:10 pm - Presentation by Aman Aalam
6:35 pm - Interactive Q&A Session7:00 pm - Networking Opportunity
7:20 PM - Closing Remarks

This event will unfold on Zoom, bringing together minds from everywhere in an inspiring virtual space.

Interested in speaking or sponsoring? Let's connect at sponsor[@torontojs.com](mailto:organizers@torontojs.com).TorontoJS is committed to creating a safe and inclusive environment for all.

Our Code of Conduct applies both online and in person at all our events and spaces.For more information on events @ TorontoJS please check out:
https://guild.host/torontojs/events

See you there!
